### Source Code
laser_get_all_intensities.jnl:
```python
'''
Read INI file and apply all laser intensities
'''

# Read variables from INI file
Get_INI_String(C:\MM\Confocal.INI,
               Laser Intensities,
               Laser_405,
               0,
               intensity_of_405)
Get_INI_String(C:\MM\Confocal.INI,
               Laser Intensities,
               Laser_445,
               0,
               intensity_of_445)
Get_INI_String(C:\MM\Confocal.INI,
               Laser Intensities,
               Laser_488,
               0,
               intensity_of_488)
Get_INI_String(C:\MM\Confocal.INI,
               Laser Intensities,
               Laser_515,
               0,
               intensity_of_515)
Get_INI_String(C:\MM\Confocal.INI,
               Laser Intensities,
               Laser_561,
               0,
               intensity_of_561)

# Apply intensities to lasers
Component_Control(Component Name = ALC Laser 1 Intensity (405nm),
                  intensity_of_405 = )
Component_Control(Component Name = ALC Laser 2 Intensity (445 nm),
                  intensity_of_445 = )
Component_Control(Component Name = ALC Laser 3 Intensity (488 nm),
                  intensity_of_488 = )
Component_Control(Component Name = ALC Laser 4 Intensity (515 nm),
                  intensity_of_515 = )
Component_Control(Component Name = ALC Laser 5 Intensity (561 nm),
                  intensity_of_561 = )
```

laser_set_405_intensity.jnl:
```python
'''
Read INI file with laser intensities, set laser intensity, and save back to
INI file
'''

# Run journal which reads from INI file and applies all laser intensities
Run_Journal(C:\MMpp\mmproc\journals\laser_get_all_intensities.jnl)

# Have the user set the correct laser intensity
Component_Control(ALC Laser 1 Intensity (405nm),
                  )

# Record the current intensity into a variable
current_laser_intensity = Component.ALC_Laser_1_Intensity__405nm_.Position

# Save this variable to INI file
Write_INI_String(IniPath = C:\MM\Confocal.INI,
                 IniSection = Laser Intensities,
                 IniKey = Laser_405,
                 current_laser_intensity = journal_time_point3)
```
